node.text:
This is really close to my heart. So many things have changed in the past year. And while I look forward to the Olympic Games, I know it is still a very challenging time for everyone out there. I am so proud to be part of @SKII STUDIO latest film #BeyondTheStadium which shines a spotlight on female entrepreneurs that have been hit hard by the pandemic.

Growing-up with a female entrepreneur myself (MOM ♥) I am thrilled to see that on top of the launch of the film, comes the 1st #ChangeDestiny Fund program in support of this community in Tokyo. Much to feel happy about - watch to learn how you can help too. #SKIIPARTNER
